<br />Actually, they probably .incbinned a whole bunch.  You should only use .db and .dw for shorter byte/word additions, because otherwise the whole code page just gets cluttered.  I'm not sure how they stored levels in SMB1, but they most certainly did at least one .incbin with all the level data in it.</div>

